@EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5190
@operatorKey = dev-secret-key

### Get available products (in stock only)
GET {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Get full machine state (products + coin float + user credit) — operator only
GET {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/state
X-Api-Key: {{operatorKey}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Load products (operator only)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/products/load
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{operatorKey}}

{
  "products": [
    { "id": "55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555", "name": "Juice", "pricePence": 120, "quantity": 5 }
  ]
}

###

### Load change (operator only)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/change/load
Content-Type: application/json
X-Api-Key: {{operatorKey}}

{
  "coins": {
    "OnePound": 20,
    "FiftyPence": 20,
    "TwentyPence": 20,
    "TenPence": 20,
    "FivePence": 20
  }
}

###

### Insert credit — £1 coin
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/credit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "denomination": "OnePound"
}

###

### Insert credit — 50p coin (build up enough for Cola)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/credit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "denomination": "FiftyPence"
}

###

### Return current credit
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/credit/return

###

### Purchase — Cola with sufficient credit (insert £1 + 50p = 150p first)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

###

### Purchase — overpayment (insert £2 first, expect 50p change)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

###

### Purchase — insufficient funds (no credit → 422)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111"
}

###

### Purchase — unknown product (→ 422)
POST {{EntrustVendingMachine.API_HostAddress}}/api/vending-machine/purchase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

###
